Copy and paste these commands on your Terminal to experience Docker faster :)

Command 1: List the docker images that exist locally on your computer/server

  docker image ls

Command 2: Search for specific nginx docker images in your repository (Docker Hub in this case)

  docker search nginx

Command 3: Download nginx image to your computer/server

  docker image pull nginx

Command 4: Inspect the specifications for the recently downloaded image

  docker image inspect nginx
